# Convention 108+ DPV Extension - RDF/Turtle Vocabulary

This file contains the RDF/Turtle serialization of the Convention 108+ DPV extension vocabulary.

**Filename**: `conv108.ttl`

**Namespace**: `1192`

**Prefix**: `conv108`

**Format**: Turtle (Terse RDF Triple Language)

**Status**: Draft v0.1 (sample)

**Last Updated**: 2025-12-29

**Ready for**: Internal review and RDF validation

---

